          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Alternatively, Edit the X-axis value of each </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> with the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-BlendPoint-X-axis-Value" styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
